These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, skiing, rugby
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | rugby | skiing | golf | snowboarding   |
| Birthday   | november  | october     | may   | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold, azalea, orchid
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dannemann, tiparillo, old-henry
1. the person who growsorchid is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | azalea | orchid | marigold | daisy    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo    | dannemann      | alhambra | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, van, boat
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, montecristo, old-henry, dunhill
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | scooter | boat | van   | jet-ski |
| Cigar   | aristoff   | old-henry | dunhill | montecristo         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, mauve, blue
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, september, may
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | blue | orange | turquise  | mauve      |
| Birthday         | april | may   | september | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, azure, coral, grey
4 different games are played: domino, whist, scrabble, go
1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Color   | grey | coral | azure | blue |
| Game    | domino       | go | scrabble | whist     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, whist, poker
City: rome, nizza, berlin, colone
1. the person playing go is on the far right##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | poker | whist | monopoly | go |
| City           | rome      | berlin | colone | nizza    |

