.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, nigerian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, swimming, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
2. the british is on the far right##1
3. the nigerian is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
5. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | spanish | british  |
| Sport           | swimming | tennis | lacrosse       | water-polo |

