.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, white, blue, lilac
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, asparagus, apricot, kale
1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person eating kale is the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Color         | blue | turquise      | white | lilac |
| Food   | cauliflower          | asparagus | apricot     | kale    |

