.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, handball, ice-hockey, skiing
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, yellow, brown
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | handball    | ice-hockey       | rugby | skiing   |
| Color     | azure | yellow | brown   | ivory |

