2. the software-developer is on the right of the designer##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Job    | designer | software-developer  | bartender | firefighter |
| Game   | chess | backgammon | scrabble          | whist    |

