2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Sport      | handball | cricket  | volleyball | sailing |
| Game   | go  | poker | scrabble           | chess   |

