1. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the modern house is on the left of the wooden house##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | billiard | canasta | domino  |
| House           | victorian | craftsman      | modern | wooden |

