4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| City   | miami | venice  | nizza | new-york   |
| Game        | backgammon | bridge | domino    | canasta |

