.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, horse, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, scooter, boat
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | goldfish | horse  | pony  | turtle |
| Transport   | helicopter   | ship | scooter | boat   |

