.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, soul, pop, blues
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, board-games, reading
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan of blues##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop | blues     | country | soul |
| Hobby         | reading | gardening | traveling   | board-games   |

