.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, chess, gardening
4 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, hamster, snake
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Hobby           | reading | gardening    | rock-climbing    | chess |
| Pet   | pony      | hamster | ferret | snake       |

