.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, hot-chocolate, juice
4 different games are played: whist, chess, mah-jongg, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is the person playing chess##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | milk      | hot-chocolate | juice | cola |
| Game     | whist | canasta    | mah-jongg  | chess |

