.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, march, october
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | fanta | mirinda | hot-chocolate | water |
| Birthday   | october     | march    | september      | december   |

