.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
House: tower, futuristic, palace, victorian
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapes, plum, cauliflower
1. the person eating garlic is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the victorian house is the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| House   | tower | palace | futuristic | victorian   |
| Food     | plum  | garlic    | grapes       | cauliflower |

 